    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Starting at 9th level, with the power of commands your powerful sight has also increased, your Eagle's Eye range increases to 60 foot radius cube. Your <em><strong>Pawns</strong></em> no longer provoke an attack of opportunity when you move them as a reaction. Additionally, you may <em><strong>Promote</strong></em> a <em><strong>Pawn</strong></em> to a <em><strong>Bishop</strong></em> by using your bonus action and a <em><strong>Brave Order</strong></em>, enemies within 15 foot radius cube of a <em><strong>Bishop</strong></em> has a penalty to attacks rolls equal to your half your Ninjutsu ability modifier (Rounded Down), this lasts a number of rounds equal to your proficiency bonus. Only one ally may be a <em><strong>Bishop</strong></em> at a time.</p>",
